Kioxia America, Inc. ("KIOXIA") respect the privacy of users who visit this website (the "Site"). This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use and share information effective as of the date posted above. By using the Site and submitting information to us you agree to the terms of this Policy.  Following the Privacy Policy is an addendum further applicable to California residents and the CCPA/CPRA legislation. To the extent there is any inadvertent conflict between the Privacy Policy and the Privacy Addendum, the Privacy Addendum controls for California residents.
